\title{Metalinguistic rationalism (definition)}
\date{2024-03-23}
\taxon{definition}

\p{A meta-vocabulary of reason relations is the right meta-vocabulary to talk about the relations between the meta-vocabularies of [logic](phil-0151), [semantics](phil-0124), and [pragmatics](phil-0102). (All three express \em{aspects} of reason giving.).}
